                                   where P is the Master Clock divider       optimal operating range. It may
f1 = (MCLK / D)                    integer value;                            be best to assign initial values of
                                   optimal f2: 90MHz< f2 <100MHz             1 to both D and P, and then by
R = f2 / f1 = xy.abcdefgh decimal                                            inspection, determine if they
